---
import { LightbulbFilament } from "phosphor-react";
---

<section class="skills py-5 py-lg-6">
  <div class="skills-inner container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Technical Skill Set</h2>
    <p class="text-muted">
      Constantly keeping myself updated with the latest tech in frontend space!
    </p>

    <div class="skills-grid mt-5">
      <div class="skill-item">
        <p class="skill-title pb-3">
          html <span>6 Years</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted skill-about mb-4">
          I always prefer semantic markup and keep accesibility in mind while
          writing my <code>html</code>. I keep the structure consistent so that
          it can be targeted well with CSS & can be scaled further.
        </p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>a11y</span>
          <span>html5</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-item">
        <p class="skill-title pb-3">
          CSS/SASS <span>5 Years</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted skill-about mb-4">
          I write modular & scalable CSS to design pixel-perfect websites, with
          strong layout debugging skills. Can leverage the benefits of
          frameworks like Bootstrap and Tailwind to create aesthetic and
          beautiful layouts from absolutely scratch.
        </p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>bootstrap</span>
          <span>tailwind</span>
          <span>css-in-js</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-item">
        <p class="skill-title pb-3">
          Javascript <span>2 Years</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted skill-about mb-4">
          Comfortable with DOM Manuplations and interactions, events, APIs,
          ES6/ES7 & ReactJS. Can work with any library (sort of) that has a good
          documentation!
        </p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span>es6</span>
          <span>ReactJS</span>
          <span>css-in-js</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="extra-skills d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="icon">
          <LightbulbFilament size={36} weight="duotone" />
        </div>
        <p>
          Does Googling the console errors, doing research on them and solving
          them by understanding the root cause count in as well? I think I got
          them!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @import "../styles/_mixins.scss";

  // Skills
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;

    @include break(lg) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .skill-item {
      @include card-base;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;

      .skill-title {
        font-size: var(--font-size-fluid-1);
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        line-height: 1.2;
        color: var(--accent-dark);

        span {
          position: relative;
          display: inline-flex;
          font-size: var(--font-size-1);
          padding-left: 1.5rem;
          text-transform: none;
          font-weight: 400;
          color: var(--gray-8);

          &::before {
            content: "";
            --size: 5px;
            height: var(--size);
            width: var(--size);
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: absolute;
            background: var(--gray-5);
            left: 0.75rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
          }
        }
      }

      .skill-about {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        flex: 1;
      }

      .tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;

        span {
          flex-shrink: 0;
          display: inline-flex;
          padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
          background: var(--gray-2);
          border-radius: 9999rem;
          border: 1.5px dashed var(--yellow-5);
          font-size: 0.65rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.25px;
          color: var(--gray-8);
        }
      }
    }

    .extra-skills {
      gap: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-2);
      margin-inline: auto;
      max-width: 600px;
      background: linear-gradient(
          to bottom right,
          rgba(#000, 0.88),
          rgba(#111, 0.9)
        ),
        url("/assets/html-code.jpg") center center no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      color: var(--gray-2);

      .icon {
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
